{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"URL()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/URL","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL_API\">URL API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>URL</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><em><code>URL()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/hash\"><code>hash</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/host\"><code>host</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/hostname\"><code>hostname</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/href\"><code>href</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/origin\"><code>origin</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/password\"><code>password</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/pathname\"><code>pathname</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/port\"><code>port</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/protocol\"><code>protocol</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/search\"><code>search</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/searchParams\"><code>searchParams</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/username\"><code>username</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURL\"><code>createObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/revokeObjectURL\"><code>revokeObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/toJSON\"><code>toJSON()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/toString\"><code>toString()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>URL API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong><code>URL()</code></strong> コンストラクターは、パラメーターによって定義された URL を表す、新しく生成された <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>URL</code></a> オブジェクトを返します。</span></p>\n\n<p>与えられたベース URL または結果の URL が有効な URL でない場合、JavaScript の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypeError\"><code>TypeError</code></a> 例外がスローされます。</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>注:</strong> この機能は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Worker</a> 内で利用可能です</p>\n</div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>url</em> = new URL(<em>url</em>, [<em>base</em>])\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"パラメーター","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"url\"><code>url</code></dt>\n <dd>絶対 URL または相対 URL を表す <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb\"><code>USVString</code></a>。<code>url</code> が相対 URL の場合、<code>base</code> は必須であり、ベース URL として使用されます。<code>url</code> が絶対 URL の場合、指定された <code>base</code> は無視されます。</dd>\n <dt id=\"base\"><code>base</code><em> </em><span class=\"badge inline optional\">省略可</span></dt>\n <dd><code>url</code> が相対 URL の場合に使用するベース URL を表す <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb\"><code>USVString</code></a>。 指定しない場合のデフォルトは <code>''</code> です。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\">\n<p><strong>注</strong>: 既存の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>URL</code></a> オブジェクトを <code>base</code> に使用することも可能で、オブジェクトの <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/href\" title=\"href\"><code>href</code></a> プロパティにそれ自体を文字列化します。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exceptions","title":"例外","isH3":true,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">例外</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">説明</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypeError\"><code>TypeError</code></a></td>\n   <td><code>url</code> (絶対 URL の場合) または <code>base</code> + <code>url</code> (相対 URL の場合) が、有効な URL ではありません。</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// ベース URL</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> m <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'https://developer.mozilla.org'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">URL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> m<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>                                <span class=\"token comment\">// =&gt; 'https://developer.mozilla.org/'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">URL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>m<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>                                     <span class=\"token comment\">// =&gt; 'https://developer.mozilla.org/'</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">URL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'en-US/docs'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>                      <span class=\"token comment\">// =&gt; 'https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> d <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">URL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'/en-US/docs'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>                     <span class=\"token comment\">// =&gt; 'https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs'</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">URL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'/en-US/docs'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> d<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>                     <span class=\"token comment\">// =&gt; 'https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs'</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">URL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'/en-US/docs'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>                     <span class=\"token comment\">// =&gt; 'https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs'</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">URL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'/en-US/docs'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://developer.mozilla.org/fr-FR/toto\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n                                                       <span class=\"token comment\">// =&gt; 'https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs'</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">URL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'/en-US/docs'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>                    <span class=\"token comment\">// '' は有効な URL ではないため、TypeError 例外が発生します</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">URL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'/en-US/docs'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>                        <span class=\"token comment\">// '/en-US/docs' は有効な URL ではないため、TypeError 例外が発生します</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">URL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'http://www.example.com'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>           <span class=\"token comment\">// =&gt; 'http://www.example.com/'</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">URL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'http://www.example.com'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>          <span class=\"token comment\">// =&gt; 'http://www.example.com/'</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">URL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"//foo.com\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://example.com\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>    <span class=\"token comment\">// =&gt; 'https://foo.com' (相対 URL を参照)</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#constructors\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">URL<br><small lang=\"ja\">URL.URL() の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.URL.URL","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/URL/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連項目","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>所属しているインターフェース: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>URL</code></a>。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specification"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連項目","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"URL() コンストラクターは、パラメーターによって定義された URL を表す、新しく生成された URL オブジェクトを返します。","popularity":0.0013,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"URL()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"URL()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"URL()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"URL()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"URL()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"URL()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/url/url","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/url/url/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL","title":"URL"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/URL","title":"URL()"}],"pageTitle":"URL() - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}